{"tid":2326290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯建議政府爭取接種疫苗市民到內地免檢疫","createTime":"2020-12-15T08:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T11:45:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd2e13c8faf3fcc182e1bc9c40cfed2c8bf8b35","tid":2326290,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"民建聯促請政府，盡早準備、統籌及公布有關接種疫苗的安排，以免被抹黑或引起市民混亂，又建議政府向中央爭取接種疫苗的市民，到內地可豁免14天檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員(區議會第二)李慧琼：「特區政府應主動和中央商討，如果證實有抗體的市民做了合適檢測，回到內地可以免14天檢疫安排，讓香港和內地可以恢復有序通關，未來民建聯請人大常委開會時，希望爭取這方面的安排。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416688&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=4f461213\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416688&h=13078e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416688</a>"},{"pid":"492e73df7a9def4ff2e07c6efdbb2a68cc6d23a3","tid":2326290,"uid":221343,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"贊成,最好班藍屍惹上去支那大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4c9b80190f646657ec8d24cb39092c62510bc8","tid":2326290,"uid":185656,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"不如直接去支那打啦"},{"pid":"b9333bc97982ab7d25c4b295fa1c34ac2c0be37f","tid":2326290,"uid":37058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:37:43.000Z","msg":"打支那疫苗先可以免<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c45e7ef13bc540ff89e3831f136c4f5b052107f","tid":2326290,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贊成"},{"pid":"7d943e13e30c827a8b2a65f81037ced2f4704c5a","tid":2